# Demo Charting Widget

A Experience Builder apps and widgets repository for demonstrational purposes that uses a 3rd party dependency (Apache ECharts).

## Get Started

1. Clone this repository [ArcGIS Experience Builder: Customizing and Extending | Developer & Technology Summit 2025](https://github.com/EsriDevEvents/arcgis-experience-builder-customizing-extending-ds-2025) and place the `exb-2025` directory within the `client` directory of your developer edition Experience Builder installation.
2. To install the 3rd party dependcency, in your terminal, navigate to the `chart-demo` directory and run `npm i`.
3. Navigate back to the `client` directory and execute the `npm start` command.
4. Choose the "Charting Demo" widget from the list of custom widgets from within the builder interface.
5. Configure the widget by selecting a `DataSource`.

